This page on SteamDB lists all games tagged as 'Open World'. Open World games offer players the freedom to explore vast environments, often with non-linear gameplay. Players can traverse various terrains, discover new locations, and interact with numerous characters. The open nature of these games allows for endless possibilities, from questing and combat to exploration and socializing. Players can build their own stories as they navigate the intricately designed worlds, making each experience unique.
